{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.120", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.000", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vorweg ein Wort zu den Stimmungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ihrer Meinung nach die Freiheit an den Universit\u00e4ten und in der Wissenschaft gef\u00e4hrden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie denken auch daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass inzwischen an manchen Universit\u00e4ten bestimmte Redner gar nicht mehr ohne Polizeischutz auftreten d\u00fcrfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das gef\u00e4hrdet die Freiheit in der Wissenschaft und an unseren Universit\u00e4ten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben dicke Bretter zu bohren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen den F\u00f6deralismus neu ordnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir wollen den Arbeitsmarkt fit machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.680", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir wollen unsere Schulen und Hochschulen wieder an die Spitze f\u00fchren\u00a0..."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind hehre Worte aus der Regierungserkl\u00e4rung der Kanzlerin vom 30.\u00a0November 2005."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wurden diese Ziele nach nunmehr zw\u00f6lf Jahren wenigstens ann\u00e4hernd erreicht?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.960", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sehe nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass unsere Hochschulen wieder an der Spitze sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Keine deutsche Universit\u00e4t kann mit \u00adHarvard, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oxford, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem MIT oder der ETH in Z\u00fcrich wirklich mithalten,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und an den Schulen sieht es auch nicht gut aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.440", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wieso sollen wir nun also glauben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in all den Jahren nicht gelungen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nun gelingen soll?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch immer sitzen in Deutschlands staatlichen Schulen bis zu \u00fcber 30\u00a0Kinder in einer Klasse. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.160", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anders sieht es an den Privatschulen aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort wei\u00df man, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.960", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein moderner Unterricht in einem kleinen Raum mit \u00fcber 30\u00a0Sch\u00fclern gar nicht m\u00f6glich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch immer sind viele Geb\u00e4ude marode, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das f\u00e4llt in Ihre Verantwortung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ihre Kollegen regieren in den L\u00e4ndern und wechseln vom Land in den Bund und zur\u00fcck.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es fehlen Kapazit\u00e4ten in den Turnhallen und in den Schwimmhallen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch immer gibt es zu wenige Lehrer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.400", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tausende Unterrichtsstunden fallen aus oder werden nur notd\u00fcrftig vertreten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.000", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist Ihre Politik in Bund und L\u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Masseneinwanderung von Menschen aus vorwiegend bildungsfernen Schichten wird die bestehenden Probleme in den n\u00e4chsten Jahren noch versch\u00e4rfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein Wort dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie dieses Problem angehen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lesen wir im Koalitionsvertrag."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen lesen wir von vollmundigen Ank\u00fcndigungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.280", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von \u201eInvestitions- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Ausstattungsoffensiven\u201c oder von \u201eQualit\u00e4tspakten\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als ich das gelesen habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "habe ich gedacht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.080", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie eigentlich in den Krieg ziehen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.680", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gegen wen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht gegen Ihre eigene Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mal sehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerne h\u00e4tten wir stattdessen erfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.880", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie all diese angek\u00fcndigten Offensiven und Pakte konkret umsetzen und finanzieren wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch dazu ist nur ansatzweise etwas zu erfahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Quasi als Leuchtturm ragt aus den meist nur nebul\u00f6s angedeuteten Vorhaben der Nationale Bildungsrat heraus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.000", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eben in der Ansprache der Ministerin war davon merkw\u00fcrdigerweise gar nicht die Rede."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.960", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was soll dieser Nationale Bildungsrat bewirken? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er soll offenbar in der Bildungspolitik Bund und L\u00e4ndern in Zukunft den Weg weisen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dieses Leuchtturmprojekt der Koalition ist ein alter Hut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bereits 1965 wurde mit \u00e4hnlicher Zielsetzung ein Deutscher Bildungsrat gegr\u00fcndet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.400", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens unter einer CDU-Regierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.960", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1975 ist er dann unter einer SPD-Regierung sang- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und klanglos wieder beerdigt worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind gespannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie das diesmal ausgeht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entscheidend wird vielmehr sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.400", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit welchen Experten dieser Nationale Bildungsrat besetzt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.080", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist zu bef\u00fcrchten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es dieselben sein werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.480", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bund und L\u00e4nder in Bildungsfragen schon jetzt beraten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.600", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir f\u00fcr die allgemeinbildenden Schulen jetzt brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "l\u00e4sst sich auch ohne aufwendige empirische Studien und Nationalen Bildungsrat mit wenigen Worten sagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.080", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich komme auch gleich zum Ende\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.520", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen gut ausgebildete und gut entlohnte Lehrer in ausreichender Zahl. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.880", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen ein klar gegliedertes Schulsystem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kleinere Klassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.920", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sanierte Geb\u00e4ude, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.840", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann noch Lehr- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.760", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Lernmittel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.240", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "praktikable Curricula, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.560", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerne auch Smartboards und PCs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.400", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann bitte aber auch das Personal zur Wartung; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.360", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wird meistens immer vergessen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.880", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war es eigentlich auch schon. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.200", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die zahlreichen Reformen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.240", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pakte und Offensiven und alles andere nutzen vielleicht denjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.440", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sie durchf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.680", 
   "id": "s000090", 
